    "Therefore, detailed scrutiny of titles and abstracts revealed that 1,073 articles were excluded because they did not comply with the predefined yardsticks.",
    "A comprehensive analysis was then performed for the subsequent 628 contributions.",
    "A total of 577 studies were excluded from the research because they failed to meet other inclusion criteria; 51 of these studies were excluded because they were determined to be relevant to basic inode requirements.",
